
& c-bills
 
 >> Help: C-Bills (Currency)
 -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
 C-Bills are the secondary currency in our economy. They serve the purpose of
 handling day to day expenses, such as orbital requests, renting units,
 playing the lottery, placing bounties, and certain Squad uses
 (not currently available).
 
 How do I earn C-Bills?
 ----------------------
  * Picking up data caches ('help data_caches')
  * Fueling bases ('help fueling')
  * Claiming objectives either by holding the claim, or simply destroying them
    ('help objectives').
 
 All this information was taken from this site:
 http://docs.btmux.com/index.php/Site_Frontier:Currencies
 
 See also: currency, objectives
 
